---
title: Gremolata-Crusted Cod with Roasted Mediterranean Veggies
description: This week,  we are making a ‘gremolata’ but it’s not as complicated as it might sound. An easy-to-create mixture of fresh parsley, garlic and lemon zest, gremolata is really popular in Italian cooking and this evening we’ve added some breadcrumbs to give it a bit of crunch. Buonissimo!
